    {
      "slug": "lobomar",
      "title": "LOBOMAR-",
      "category": "Assignment",
      "date": "2024-10-01",
      "gridOrder": 2,
      "gridStyle": "wide",
      "thumbnail": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/67a39066c276671b47c91c55/67a39109657b4c729ef63200_Lobomar_Caps_V4_21Oct2024_L1000379_76b481f4-445a-49bc-89a1-05bfb22eb61a.jpg.avif",
      "description": [
        {
          "_type": "block",
          "_key": "block0",
          "style": "normal",
          "markDefs": [],
          "children": [
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x0",
              "text": "CLIENT:",
              "marks": ["strong"]
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x1",
              "text": " LOBOMAR-\n",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x2",
              "text": "CLIENT INTEL:",
              "marks": ["strong"]
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x3",
              "text": " Founded by siblings Marcella and Marco Lobo in 2023, LOBOMAR- was born from a life lived between Köln, London, and Amsterdam. With Indian-Italian roots, the duo built a brand that questions rigid definitions of identity—celebrating the fluidity of personal expression and the cultural layering that shapes it.\n",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x4",
              "text": "SUBJECT:",
              "marks": ["strong"]
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x5",
              "text": " New collection of headwear\n",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x6",
              "text": "BRIEF:",
              "marks": ["strong"]
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x7",
              "text": " Capture the brand’s latest capsule of upcycled caps, made from reclaimed sarees sourced in Mumbai.\n",
              "marks": []
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x8",
              "text": "APPROACH:",
              "marks": ["strong"]
            },
            {
              "_type": "span",
              "_key": "span0x9",
              "text": " To spotlight the intricate patterns and tactile richness of the sarees, we used contrasting tones and defined shadows—amplifying the sculptural quality of the caps. The editorial narrative unfolds around a late-night dinner among friends, echoing LOBOMAR-’s emphasis on community, connection, and the warmth found in shared rituals.",
              "marks": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
