  "about": {
    "title": "About",
    "text": "Kaijo Studio is a creative photography studio crafting imagery that merges the commercial with the artistic. We create photos that convey the identity of both your brand and your products with daring visual direction and a gentle eye.",
    "secondText": "Founded by photographer Joep Hijwegen and producer Kathy Sihavong, Kaijo is a strange beast: part production house, part creative partner. We collaborate with small brands to shape visuals that sell both a product and a vision. As a small team with a multidisciplinary background, we are able to translate your vision forcefully without dilution.",
